%html
  %head
    %meta{:charset => 'utf-8'}
    %title HTML + CSS level 1 « SVC Seattle
    %link{:rel => 'stylesheet', :href => '/svc/css/lib/twitter-bootstrap.min.css'}
    %link{:rel => 'stylesheet', :href => '/svc/css/styles.css' }

  %body
    #top.topbar
      .topbar-inner
        .container
          %h3
            %a{:href => 'https://www.svcseattle.com/classes/html-and-css-level-1-reedy-winter-2012'}
              School of Visual Concepts
          %ul.nav
            %li.active
              %a{:href => '#overview'} Overview
            %li
              %a{:href => '#instructor'} Instructor
            %li
              %a{:href => '#course-description'} Course Description
            %li
              %a{:href => '#course-materials'} Course Materials
            %li.dropdown{:data => {:dropdown => true}}
              %a.dropdown-toggle{:href => '#'} Jump to Week
              %ul.dropdown-menu
                %li
                  %a{:href => '#week-1'} Week 1
                %li
                  %a{:href => '#week-2'} Week 2
                %li
                  %a{:href => '#week-3'} Week 3
                %li
                  %a{:href => '#week-4'} Week 4
                %li
                  %a{:href => '#week-5'} Week 5

    %header.jumbotron.masthead
      .inner
        .grid
        .container
          %h1
            HTML & CSS
            %small Level 1
          %p
            Learning the basics of
            %abbr{:title => 'HyperText Markup Language'} HTML
            &
            %abbr{:title => 'Cascading StyleSheets'} CSS
            for fun and profit!

    %section#overview
      .container
        .row
          %section#instructor.span3
            %h1 Instructor
            %h2 Dallas Reedy
            %img{:src => 'images/dallas-head-shot.jpg', :width => 400, :height => 400, :alt => (alt = 'Dallas Reedy'), :title => alt}
            %dl
              %dt email
              %dd
                %a{:href => 'mailto:dallas@dallasreedy.com'} dallas@dallasreedy.com

              %dt web
              %dd
                %a{:href => 'http://dallasreedy.com/'} dallasreedy.com

          %section#course-description.span6
            %h1 Course Description
            %p
              HTML and CSS are the fundamental building blocks of the web. They are essential 
              concepts to understand for many of today’s careers. Luckily, they are also fun and 
              easy to learn! In this course, we’ll be starting from the beginning and building up a 
              solid, practical foundation in these symbiotic web languages.

          %section#course-materials.span7
            %h1 Course Materials
            .row
              .span5.offset2
                %h2
                  HTML5 & CSS: Visual QuickStart Guide
                  %small (7th Edition)
                %h3
                  by
                  %span.author Elizabeth Castro
                  &
                  %span.author Bruce Hyslop
              %img{:src => 'images/HTML5-and-CSS3.jpg', :width => 502, :height => 648, :alt => (alt = 'HTML5 and CSS3: Visual QuickStart'), :title => alt}

    %script{:src => 'js/lib/jquery-1.7.1.min.js'}
    %script{:src => 'js/lib/twitter-bootstrap/dropdown.js'}
